  91     public HPlusSupport(DeviceType type) {                                                               
  92         super(LOG);                                                                                      
  93         LOG.info("HPlusSupport Instance Created");                                                       
  94         deviceType = type;                                                                               
  95                                                                                                          
  96         addSupportedService(HPlusConstants.UUID_SERVICE_HP);                                             
  97                                                                                                          
  98         LocalBroadcastManager broadcastManager = LocalBroadcastManager.getInstance(getContext());        
  99         IntentFilter intentFilter = new IntentFilter();                                                  
 100                                                                                                          
 101         broadcastManager.registerReceiver(mReceiver, intentFilter);                                      
 102     }

 115     @Override                                                                                            
 116     protected TransactionBuilder initializeDevice(TransactionBuilder builder) {                          
 117         LOG.info("Initializing");                                                                        
 118                                                                                                          
 119         gbDevice.setState(GBDevice.State.INITIALIZING);                                                  
 120         gbDevice.sendDeviceUpdateIntent(getContext());                                                   
 121                                                                                                          
 122         measureCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE);           
 123         ctrlCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_CONTROL);              
 124                                                                                                          
 125                                                                                                          
 126         builder.notify(getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE), true);             
 127         builder.setGattCallback(this);                                                                   
 128         builder.notify(measureCharacteristic, true);                                                     
 129         //Initialize device                                                                              
 130         sendUserInfo(builder); //Sync preferences                                                        
 131                                                                                                          
 132         gbDevice.setState(GBDevice.State.INITIALIZED);                                                   
 133         gbDevice.sendDeviceUpdateIntent(getContext());                                                   
 134                                                                                                          
 135         if(syncHelper == null) {                                                                         
 136             syncHelper = new HPlusHandlerThread(getDevice(), getContext(), this);                        
 137             syncHelper.start();                                                                          
 138         }                                                                                                
 139         syncHelper.sync();                                                                               
 140                                                                                                          
 141         getDevice().setFirmwareVersion("N/A");                                                           
 142         getDevice().setFirmwareVersion2("N/A");                                                          
 143                                                                                                          
 144         requestDeviceInfo(builder);                                                                      
 145                                                                                                          
 146         LOG.info("Initialization Done");                                                                 
 147                                                                                                          
 148         return builder;                                                                                  
 149     }

 151     private HPlusSupport sendUserInfo(TransactionBuilder builder) {                                      
 152         builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_PREF_START);                            
 153         builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_PREF_START1);                           
 154                                                                                                          
 155         syncPreferences(builder);                                                                        
 156                                                                                                          
 157         builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_CONF_END});                  
 158         return this;                                                                                     
 159     }

 161     private HPlusSupport syncPreferences(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                               
 162                                                                                                          
 163         if (deviceType == DeviceType.HPLUS) {                                                            
 164             setSIT(transaction);          //Sync SIT Interval                                            
 165         }                                                                                                
 166                                                                                                          
 167         setCurrentDate(transaction);                                                                     
 168         setCurrentTime(transaction);                                                                     
 169         setDayOfWeek(transaction);                                                                       
 170         setTimeMode(transaction);                                                                        
 171                                                                                                          
 172         setGender(transaction);                                                                          
 173         setAge(transaction);                                                                             
 174         setWeight(transaction);                                                                          
 175         setHeight(transaction);                                                                          
 176                                                                                                          
 177         setGoal(transaction);                                                                            
 178         setLanguage(transaction);                                                                        
 179         setScreenTime(transaction);                                                                      
 180         setUnit(transaction);                                                                            
 181         setAllDayHeart(transaction);                                                                     
 182                                                                                                          
 183         return this;                                                                                     
 184     }

 215     private HPlusSupport setCurrentDate(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                
 216         Calendar c = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                    
 217         int year = c.get(Calendar.YEAR);                                                                 
 218         int month = c.get(Calendar.MONTH);                                                               
 219         int day = c.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH);                                                          
 220                                                                                                          
 221         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                
 222                 HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_DATE,                                                             
 223                 (byte) ((year / 256) & 0xff),                                                            
 224                 (byte) (year % 256),                                                                     
 225                 (byte) (month + 1),                                                                      
 226                 (byte) (day)                                                                             
 227                                                                                                          
 228         });                                                                                              
 229         return this;                                                                                     
 230     }                                                                                                    
 231                                                                                                          
 232     private HPlusSupport setCurrentTime(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                
 233         Calendar c = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                    
 234                                                                                                          
 235         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                
 236                 HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_TIME,                                                             
 237                 (byte) c.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY),                                                      
 238                 (byte) c.get(Calendar.MINUTE),                                                           
 239                 (byte) c.get(Calendar.SECOND)

 257     private HPlusSupport setSIT(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                        
 258                                                                                                          
 259         //Makibes F68 doesn't like this command.                                                         
 260         //Just ignore.                                                                                   
 261         if (deviceType == DeviceType.MAKIBESF68) {                                                       
 262             return this;                                                                                 
 263         }                                                                                                
 264                                                                                                          
 265         int startTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITStartTime(getDevice().getAddress());                      
 266         int endTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITEndTime(getDevice().getAddress());                          
 267                                                                                                          
 268         Calendar now = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                  
 269                                                                                                          
 270         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                
 271                 HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_SIT_INTERVAL,                                                     
 272                 (byte) ((startTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                       
 273                 (byte) (startTime % 256),                                                                
 274                 (byte) ((endTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                         
 275                 (byte) (endTime % 256),                                                                  
 276                 0,                                                                                       
 277                 0,                                                                                       
 278                 (byte) ((now.get(Calendar.YEAR) / 256) & 0xff),                                          
 279                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.YEAR) % 256),                                                   
 280                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MONTH) + 1),                                                    
 281                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH)),                                                 
 282                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY)),                                                  
 283                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MINUTE)),                                                       
 284                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.SECOND)),                                                       
 285                 0,                                                                                       
 286                 0,                                                                                       
 287                 0,                                                                                       
 288                 0                                                                                        
 289                                                                                                          
 290         });                                                                                              
 291         return this;                                                                                     
 292     }

 372     private HPlusSupport setAlarm(TransactionBuilder transaction, Calendar t) {                          
 373                                                                                                          
 374         byte hour = HPlusConstants.ARG_ALARM_DISABLE;                                                    
 375         byte minute = HPlusConstants.ARG_ALARM_DISABLE;                                                  
 376                                                                                                          
 377         if (t != null) {                                                                                 
 378             hour = (byte) t.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY);                                                   
 379             minute = (byte) t.get(Calendar.MINUTE);                                                      
 380         }                                                                                                
 381                                                                                                          
 382         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_ALARM,                   
 383                 hour,                                                                                    
 384                 minute});                                                                                
 385                                                                                                          
 386         return this;                                                                                     
 387     }

 479             }                                                                                            
 480                                                                                                          
 481             setAlarm(builder, null);                                                                     
 482             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 483                                                                                                          
 484             GB.toast(getContext(), getContext().getString(R.string.user_feedback_all_alarms_disabled), To🔵
 485         } catch (Exception e) {

 717     private void showIncomingCall(String name, String rawNumber) {                                       
 718         try {                                                                                            
 719                                                                                                          
 720             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("incomingCall");                             
 721                                                                                                          
 722             //Enable call notifications                                                                  
 723             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_INCOMING_CALL, 1});   
 724                                                                                                          
 725             //Show Call Icon                                                                             
 726             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_CALL, HPlusConst🔵
 727                                                                                                          
 728             if(name != null) {                                                                           
 729                 byte[] msg = new byte[13];                                                               
 730                                                                                                          
 731                 //Show call name                                                                         
 732                 for (int i = 0; i < msg.length; i++)                                                     
 733                     msg[i] = ' ';                                                                        
 734                                                                                                          
 735                 byte[] nameBytes = encodeStringToDevice(name);                                           
 736                 for (int i = 0; i < nameBytes.length && i < (msg.length - 1); i++)                       
 737                     msg[i + 1] = nameBytes[i];                                                           
 738                                                                                                          
 739                 msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT_NAME;                                    
 740                 builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                  
 741                                                                                                          
 742                 msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT_NAME_CN;                                 
 743                 builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                  
 744             }                                                                                            
 745                                                                                                          
 746             if(rawNumber != null) {                                                                      
 747                 StringBuilder number = new StringBuilder();                                              
 748                                                                                                          
 749                 //Clean up number as the device only accepts digits                                      
 750                 for (char c : rawNumber.toCharArray()) {                                                 
 751                     if (Character.isDigit(c)) {                                                          
 752                         number.append(c);                                                                
 753                     }                                                                                    
 754                 }                                                                                        
 755                                                                                                          
 756                 byte[] msg = new byte[13];                                                               
 757                                                                                                          
 758                 //Show call number                                                                       
 759                 for (int i = 0; i < msg.length; i++)                                                     
 760                     msg[i] = ' ';                                                                        
 761                                                                                                          
 762                 for (int i = 0; i < number.length() && i < (msg.length - 1); i++)                        
 763                     msg[i + 1] = (byte) number.charAt(i);                                                
 764                                                                                                          
 765                 msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_CALL_NUMBER;                                    
 766                                                                                                          
 767                 builder.wait(200);                                                                       
 768                 builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                  
 769             }                                                                                            
 770                                                                                                          
 771             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 772         } catch (IOException e) {                                                                        
 773             GB.toast(getContext(), "Error showing incoming call: " + e.getLocalizedMessage(), Toast.LENGT🔵
 774                                                                                                          
 775         }                                                                                                
 776     }

 778     private void showText(String title, String body) {                                                   
 779         try {                                                                                            
 780             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("notification");                             
 781                                                                                                          
 782             String message = "";                                                                         
 783                                                                                                          
 784             if (title != null && title.length() > 0) {                                                   
 785                 message = StringUtils.pad(StringUtils.truncate(title, 16), 16); //Limit title to top row 
 786             }                                                                                            
 787                                                                                                          
 788             if (body != null) {                                                                          
 789                 message += body;                                                                         
 790             }                                                                                            
 791                                                                                                          
 792             byte[] messageBytes = encodeStringToDevice(message);                                         
 793                                                                                                          
 794             int length = messageBytes.length / 17;                                                       
 795                                                                                                          
 796             length = length > 5 ? 5 : length;                                                            
 797                                                                                                          
 798             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_MESSAGE, HPlusCo🔵
 799                                                                                                          
 800             int remaining = Math.min(255, (messageBytes.length % 17 > 0) ? length + 1 : length);         
 801                                                                                                          
 802             byte[] msg = new byte[20];                                                                   
 803             msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT;                                             
 804             msg[1] = (byte) remaining;                                                                   
 805                                                                                                          
 806             for (int i = 2; i < msg.length; i++)                                                         
 807                 msg[i] = ' ';                                                                            
 808                                                                                                          
 809             int message_index = 0;                                                                       
 810             int i = 3;                                                                                   
 811                                                                                                          
 812             for (int j = 0; j < messageBytes.length; j++) {                                              
 813                 msg[i++] = messageBytes[j];                                                              
 814                                                                                                          
 815                 if (i == msg.length) {                                                                   
 816                     message_index++;                                                                     
 817                     msg[2] = (byte) message_index;                                                       
 818                     builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                              
 819                                                                                                          
 820                     msg = msg.clone();                                                                   
 821                     for (i = 3; i < msg.length; i++)                                                     
 822                         msg[i] = ' ';                                                                    
 823                                                                                                          
 824                     if (message_index < remaining)                                                       
 825                         i = 3;                                                                           
 826                     else                                                                                 
 827                         break;                                                                           
 828                 }                                                                                        
 829             }                                                                                            
 830                                                                                                          
 831             msg[2] = (byte) remaining;                                                                   
 832                                                                                                          
 833             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                      
 834             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 835         } catch (IOException e) {                                                                        
 836             GB.toast(getContext(), "Error showing device Notification: " + e.getLocalizedMessage(), Toast🔵
 837                                                                                                          
 838         }                                                                                                
 839     }

 849     /**                                                                                                  
 850      * HPlus devices accept a subset of GB2312 with some modifications.                                  
 851      * This function will apply a custom transliteration.                                                
 852      * While related to the methods implemented in LanguageUtils. These are specific for HPLUS           
 853      *                                                                                                   
 854      * @param s The String to transliterate                                                              
 855      * @return An array of bytes ready to be sent to the device                                          
 856      */                                                                                                  
 857     private byte[] encodeStringToDevice(String s) {                                                      
 858                                                                                                          
 859         List<Byte> outBytes = new ArrayList<Byte>();                                                     
 860                                                                                                          
 861         for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {                                                           
 862             Character c = s.charAt(i);                                                                   
 863             byte[] cs;                                                                                   
 864                                                                                                          
 865             if (HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.containsKey(c)) {                                        
 866                 cs = HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.get(c);                                             
 867             } else {                                                                                     
 868                 try {                                                                                    
 869                     if(HPlusCoordinator.getUnicodeSupport(this.gbDevice.getAddress()))                   
 870                         cs = c.toString().getBytes("Unicode");                                           
 871                     else                                                                                 
 872                         cs = c.toString().getBytes("GB2312");                                            
 873                 } catch (UnsupportedEncodingException e) {                                               
 874                     //Fallback. Result string may be strange, but better than nothing                    
 875                     cs = c.toString().getBytes();                                                        
 876                 }                                                                                        
 877             }                                                                                            
 878             for (int j = 0; j < cs.length; j++)                                                          
 879                 outBytes.add(cs[j]);                                                                     
 880         }                                                                                                
 881                                                                                                          
 882         return ArrayUtils.toPrimitive(outBytes.toArray(new Byte[outBytes.size()]));                      
 883     }

 885     @Override                                                                                            
 886     public boolean onCharacteristicChanged(BluetoothGatt gatt,                                           
 887                                            BluetoothGattCharacteristic characteristic) {                 
 888         if (super.onCharacteristicChanged(gatt, characteristic)) {                                       
 889             return true;                                                                                 
 890         }                                                                                                
 891                                                                                                          
 892         UUID characteristicUUID = characteristic.getUuid();                                              
 893         byte[] data = characteristic.getValue();                                                         
 894         if (data.length == 0)                                                                            
 895             return true;                                                                                 
 896                                                                                                          
 897         switch (data[0]) {                                                                               
 898             case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION:                                                            
 899             case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION1:                                                           
 900                 return syncHelper.processVersion(data);                                                  
 901                                                                                                          
 902             case HPlusConstants.DATA_STATS:                                                              
 903                 boolean result = syncHelper.processRealtimeStats(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAge());   
 904                 if (result) {                                                                            
 905                     processExtraInfo (data);                                                             
 906                 }                                                                                        
 907                 return result;                                                                           
 908                                                                                                          
 909             case HPlusConstants.DATA_SLEEP:                                                              
 910                 return syncHelper.processIncomingSleepData(data);                                        
 911                                                                                                          
 912             case HPlusConstants.DATA_STEPS:                                                              
 913                 return syncHelper.processDaySummary(data);                                               
 914                                                                                                          
 915             case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY:                                                        
 916             case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY_ALT:                                                    
 917                 return syncHelper.processIncomingDaySlotData(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAge());       
 918             case HPlusConstants.DATA_UNKNOWN:                                                            
 919                 return true;                                                                             
 920             default:                                                                                     
 921                                                                                                          
 922                 LOG.info("Unhandled characteristic change: " + characteristicUUID + " code: " + Arrays.to🔵
 923                 return true;                                                                             
 924         }                                                                                                
 925     }

 927     private void  processExtraInfo (byte[] data) {                                                       
 928         try {                                                                                            
 929             HPlusDataRecordRealtime record = new HPlusDataRecordRealtime(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAg🔵
 930                                                                                                          
 931             handleBatteryInfo(record.battery);                                                           
 932                                                                                                          
 933             String DEVINFO_STEP = getContext().getString(R.string.chart_steps) + ": ";                   
 934             String DEVINFO_DISTANCE = getContext().getString(R.string.distance) + ": ";                  
 935             String DEVINFO_CALORY = getContext().getString(R.string.calories) + ": ";                    
 936             String DEVINFO_HEART = getContext().getString(R.string.charts_legend_heartrate);             
 937                                                                                                          
 938             String info = "";                                                                            
 939             if (record.steps > 0) {                                                                      
 940                 info += DEVINFO_STEP + String.valueOf(record.steps) + "   ";                             
 941             }                                                                                            
 942             if (record.distance > 0) {                                                                   
 943                 info += DEVINFO_DISTANCE + String.valueOf(record.distance) + "   ";                      
 944             }                                                                                            
 945             if (record.calories > 0) {                                                                   
 946                 info += DEVINFO_CALORY + String.valueOf(record.calories) + "   ";                        
 947             }                                                                                            
 948             if (record.heartRate > 0) {                                                                  
 949                 info += DEVINFO_HEART + String.valueOf(record.heartRate) + "   ";                        
 950             }                                                                                            
 951                                                                                                          
 952             if (!info.equals("")) {                                                                      
 953                 getDevice().addDeviceInfo(new GenericItem("", info));                                    
 954             }                                                                                            
 955         } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {                                                           
 956             LOG.info((e.getMessage()));                                                                  
 957         }                                                                                                
 958     }

 962                 batteryCmd.level = (short) data;                                                         
 963                 handleGBDeviceEvent(batteryCmd);                                                         
 964             }                                                                                            
 965     }

 121                                                                                                          
 122         measureCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE);           
 123         ctrlCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_CONTROL);              
 124                                                                                                          
 125                                                                                                          
 126         builder.notify(getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE), true);             
 127         builder.setGattCallback(this);                                                                   
 128         builder.notify(measureCharacteristic, true);                                                     
 129         //Initialize device                                                                              
 130         sendUserInfo(builder); //Sync preferences                                                        
 131                                                                                                          
 132         gbDevice.setState(GBDevice.State.INITIALIZED);                                                   
 133         gbDevice.sendDeviceUpdateIntent(getContext());                                                   
 134                                                                                                          
 135         if(syncHelper == null) {                                                                         
 136             syncHelper = new HPlusHandlerThread(getDevice(), getContext(), this);                        
 137             syncHelper.start();                                                                          
 138         }                                                                                                
 139         syncHelper.sync();                                                                               
 140                                                                                                          
 141         getDevice().setFirmwareVersion("N/A");                                                           
 142         getDevice().setFirmwareVersion2("N/A");                                                          
 143                                                                                                          
 144         requestDeviceInfo(builder);                                                                      
 145                                                                                                          
 146         LOG.info("Initialization Done");                                                                 
 147                                                                                                          
 148         return builder;                                                                                  
 149     }

 151     private HPlusSupport sendUserInfo(TransactionBuilder builder) {                                      
 152         builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_PREF_START);                            
 153         builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_PREF_START1);

 156

 158         return this;

 215     private HPlusSupport setCurrentDate(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                
 216         Calendar c = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                    
 217         int year = c.get(Calendar.YEAR);                                                                 
 218         int month = c.get(Calendar.MONTH);                                                               
 219         int day = c.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH);                                                          
 220                                                                                                          
 221         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                
 222                 HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_DATE,                                                             
 223                 (byte) ((year / 256) & 0xff),                                                            
 224                 (byte) (year % 256),                                                                     
 225                 (byte) (month + 1),                                                                      
 226                 (byte) (day)                                                                             
 227                                                                                                          
 228         });                                                                                              
 229         return this;                                                                                     
 230     }

 257     private HPlusSupport setSIT(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                        
 258                                                                                                          
 259         //Makibes F68 doesn't like this command.                                                         
 260         //Just ignore.                                                                                   
 261         if (deviceType == DeviceType.MAKIBESF68) {                                                       
 262             return this;                                                                                 
 263         }                                                                                                
 264                                                                                                          
 265         int startTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITStartTime(getDevice().getAddress());                      
 266         int endTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITEndTime(getDevice().getAddress());                          
 267                                                                                                          
 268         Calendar now = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                  
 269                                                                                                          
 270         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                
 271                 HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_SIT_INTERVAL,                                                     
 272                 (byte) ((startTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                       
 273                 (byte) (startTime % 256),                                                                
 274                 (byte) ((endTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                         
 275                 (byte) (endTime % 256),                                                                  
 276                 0,                                                                                       
 277                 0,                                                                                       
 278                 (byte) ((now.get(Calendar.YEAR) / 256) & 0xff),                                          
 279                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.YEAR) % 256),                                                   
 280                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MONTH) + 1),                                                    
 281                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH)),                                                 
 282                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY)),                                                  
 283                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MINUTE)),                                                       
 284                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.SECOND)),                                                       
 285                 0,                                                                                       
 286                 0,                                                                                       
 287                 0,                                                                                       
 288                 0                                                                                        
 289                                                                                                          
 290         });                                                                                              
 291         return this;                                                                                     
 292     }

 449                                                                                                          
 450                                                                                                          
 451         try {                                                                                            
 452             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("alarm");                                    
 453                                                                                                          
 454             for (Alarm alarm : alarms) {                                                                 
 455                                                                                                          
 456                 if (!alarm.isEnabled())                                                                  
 457                     continue;                                                                            
 458                                                                                                          
 459                 if (alarm.isSmartWakeup()) //Not available                                               
 460                     continue;

 463                 setAlarm(builder, t);                                                                    
 464                 builder.queue(getQueue());                                                               
 465                                                                                                          
 466                 GB.toast(getContext(), getContext().getString(R.string.user_feedback_miband_set_alarms_ok🔵
 467                                                                                                          
 468                 return; //Only first alarm                                                               
 469             }                                                                                            
 470                                                                                                          
 471             setAlarm(builder, null);                                                                     
 472             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 473                                                                                                          
 474             GB.toast(getContext(), getContext().getString(R.string.user_feedback_all_alarms_disabled), To🔵
 475         } catch (Exception e) {                                                                          
 476         }                                                                                                
 477                                                                                                          
 478                                                                                                          
 479     }

 669     private void showIncomingCall(String name, String rawNumber) {                                       
 670         try {                                                                                            
 671                                                                                                          
 672             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("incomingCall");                             
 673                                                                                                          
 674             //Enable call notifications                                                                  
 675             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_INCOMING_CALL, 1});   
 676                                                                                                          
 677             //Show Call Icon                                                                             
 678             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_CALL, HPlusConst🔵
 679                                                                                                          
 680             if(name != null) {                                                                           
 681             byte[] msg = new byte[13];                                                                   
 682                                                                                                          
 683             //Show call name                                                                             
 684             for (int i = 0; i < msg.length; i++)                                                         
 685                 msg[i] = ' ';                                                                            
 686                                                                                                          
 687             byte[] nameBytes = encodeStringToDevice(name);                                               
 688             for (int i = 0; i < nameBytes.length && i < (msg.length - 1); i++)                           
 689                 msg[i + 1] = nameBytes[i];                                                               
 690                                                                                                          
 691             msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT_NAME;                                        
 692             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                      
 693                                                                                                          
 694             msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT_NAME_CN;                                     
 695             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                      
 696             }                                                                                            
 697                                                                                                          
 698             if(rawNumber != null) {                                                                      
 699                 StringBuilder number = new StringBuilder();                                              
 700                                                                                                          
 701                 //Clean up number as the device only accepts digits                                      
 702                 for (char c : rawNumber.toCharArray()) {                                                 
 703                     if (Character.isDigit(c)) {                                                          
 704                         number.append(c);                                                                
 705                     }                                                                                    
 706                 }                                                                                        
 707                                                                                                          
 708                 byte[] msg = new byte[13];                                                               
 709                                                                                                          
 710             //Show call number                                                                           
 711             for (int i = 0; i < msg.length; i++)                                                         
 712                 msg[i] = ' ';                                                                            
 713                                                                                                          
 714             for (int i = 0; i < number.length() && i < (msg.length - 1); i++)                            
 715                 msg[i + 1] = (byte) number.charAt(i);                                                    
 716                                                                                                          
 717             msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_CALL_NUMBER;                                        
 718                                                                                                          
 719                 builder.wait(200);                                                                       
 720             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                      
 721             }                                                                                            
 722                                                                                                          
 723             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 724         } catch (IOException e) {                                                                        
 725             GB.toast(getContext(), "Error showing incoming call: " + e.getLocalizedMessage(), Toast.LENGT🔵
 726                                                                                                          
 727         }                                                                                                
 728     }                                                                                                    
 729                                                                                                          
 730     private void showText(String title, String body) {                                                   
 731         try {                                                                                            
 732             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("notification");                             
 733                                                                                                          
 734             String message = "";                                                                         
 735                                                                                                          
 736             if (title != null && title.length() > 0) {                                                   
 737                 message = StringUtils.pad(StringUtils.truncate(title, 16), 16); //Limit title to top row 
 738             }                                                                                            
 739                                                                                                          
 740             if (body != null) {                                                                          
 741                 message += body;                                                                         
 742             }                                                                                            
 743                                                                                                          
 744             byte[] messageBytes = encodeStringToDevice(message);                                         
 745                                                                                                          
 746             int length = messageBytes.length / 17;                                                       
 747                                                                                                          
 748             length = length > 5 ? 5 : length;                                                            
 749                                                                                                          
 750             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_MESSAGE, HPlusCo🔵
 751                                                                                                          
 752             int remaining = Math.min(255, (messageBytes.length % 17 > 0) ? length + 1 : length);         
 753                                                                                                          
 754             byte[] msg = new byte[20];                                                                   
 755             msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT;                                             
 756             msg[1] = (byte) remaining;                                                                   
 757                                                                                                          
 758             for (int i = 2; i < msg.length; i++)                                                         
 759                 msg[i] = ' ';                                                                            
 760                                                                                                          
 761             int message_index = 0;                                                                       
 762             int i = 3;                                                                                   
 763                                                                                                          
 764             for (int j = 0; j < messageBytes.length; j++) {                                              
 765                 msg[i++] = messageBytes[j];                                                              
 766                                                                                                          
 767                 if (i == msg.length) {                                                                   
 768                     message_index++;                                                                     
 769                     msg[2] = (byte) message_index;                                                       
 770                     builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                              
 771                                                                                                          
 772                     msg = msg.clone();                                                                   
 773                     for (i = 3; i < msg.length; i++)                                                     
 774                         msg[i] = ' ';                                                                    
 775                                                                                                          
 776                     if (message_index < remaining)                                                       
 777                         i = 3;                                                                           
 778                     else                                                                                 
 779                         break;                                                                           
 780                 }                                                                                        
 781             }                                                                                            
 782                                                                                                          
 783             msg[2] = (byte) remaining;                                                                   
 784                                                                                                          
 785             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                      
 786             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 787         } catch (IOException e) {                                                                        
 788             GB.toast(getContext(), "Error showing device Notification: " + e.getLocalizedMessage(), Toast🔵
 789                                                                                                          
 790         }                                                                                                
 791     }

 794         if (syncHelper != null) {                                                                        
 795             syncHelper.quit();                                                                           
 796             syncHelper.interrupt();                                                                      
 797             syncHelper = null;                                                                           
 798         }                                                                                                
 799     }

 801     /**                                                                                                  
 802      * HPlus devices accept a subset of GB2312 with some modifications.                                  
 803      * This function will apply a custom transliteration.                                                
 804      * While related to the methods implemented in LanguageUtils. These are specific for HPLUS           
 805      *                                                                                                   
 806      * @param s The String to transliterate                                                              
 807      * @return An array of bytes ready to be sent to the device                                          
 808      */                                                                                                  
 809     private byte[] encodeStringToDevice(String s) {                                                      
 810                                                                                                          
 811         List<Byte> outBytes = new ArrayList<Byte>();                                                     
 812                                                                                                          
 813         for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {                                                           
 814             Character c = s.charAt(i);                                                                   
 815             byte[] cs;                                                                                   
 816                                                                                                          
 817             if (HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.containsKey(c)) {                                        
 818                 cs = HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.get(c);                                             
 819             } else {                                                                                     
 820                 try {                                                                                    
 821                     if(HPlusCoordinator.getUnicodeSupport(this.gbDevice.getAddress()))                   
 822                         cs = c.toString().getBytes("Unicode");                                           
 823                     else                                                                                 
 824                         cs = c.toString().getBytes("GB2312");                                            
 825                 } catch (UnsupportedEncodingException e) {                                               
 826                     //Fallback. Result string may be strange, but better than nothing                    
 827                     cs = c.toString().getBytes();                                                        
 828                 }                                                                                        
 829             }                                                                                            
 830             for (int j = 0; j < cs.length; j++)                                                          
 831                 outBytes.add(cs[j]);                                                                     
 832         }                                                                                                
 833                                                                                                          
 834         return ArrayUtils.toPrimitive(outBytes.toArray(new Byte[outBytes.size()]));                      
 835     }
