 837     @Override                                                                                            
 838     public boolean onCharacteristicChanged(BluetoothGatt gatt,                                           
 839                                            BluetoothGattCharacteristic characteristic) {                 
 840         if (super.onCharacteristicChanged(gatt, characteristic)) {                                       
 841             return true;                                                                                 
 842         }                                                                                                
 843                                                                                                          
 844         UUID characteristicUUID = characteristic.getUuid();                                              
 845         byte[] data = characteristic.getValue();                                                         
 846         if (data.length == 0)                                                                            
 847             return true;                                                                                 
 848                                                                                                          
 849         switch (data[0]) {                                                                               
 850             case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION:                                                            
 851             case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION1:                                                           
 852                 return syncHelper.processVersion(data);                                                  
 853                                                                                                          
 854             case HPlusConstants.DATA_STATS:                                                              
 855                 boolean result = syncHelper.processRealtimeStats(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAge());   
 856                 if (result) {                                                                            
 857                     processExtraInfo (data);                                                             
 858                 }                                                                                        
 859                 return result;                                                                           
 860                                                                                                          
 861             case HPlusConstants.DATA_SLEEP:                                                              
 862                 return syncHelper.processIncomingSleepData(data);                                        
 863                                                                                                          
 864             case HPlusConstants.DATA_STEPS:                                                              
 865                 return syncHelper.processDaySummary(data);                                               
 866                                                                                                          
 867             case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY:                                                        
 868             case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY_ALT:                                                    
 869                 return syncHelper.processIncomingDaySlotData(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAge());       
 870             case HPlusConstants.DATA_UNKNOWN:                                                            
 871                 return true;                                                                             
 872             default:                                                                                     
 873                                                                                                          
 874                 LOG.info("Unhandled characteristic change: " + characteristicUUID + " code: " + Arrays.to🔵
 875                 return true;                                                                             
 876         }                                                                                                
 877     }                                                                                                    
 878                                                                                                          
 879     private void  processExtraInfo (byte[] data) {                                                       
 880         try {                                                                                            
 881             HPlusDataRecordRealtime record = new HPlusDataRecordRealtime(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAg🔵
 882                                                                                                          
 883             handleBatteryInfo(record.battery);                                                           
 884                                                                                                          
 885             String DEVINFO_STEP = getContext().getString(R.string.chart_steps) + ": ";                   
 886             String DEVINFO_DISTANCE = getContext().getString(R.string.distance) + ": ";                  
 887             String DEVINFO_CALORY = getContext().getString(R.string.calories) + ": ";                    
 888             String DEVINFO_HEART = getContext().getString(R.string.charts_legend_heartrate);             
 889                                                                                                          
 890             String info = "";                                                                            
 891             if (record.steps > 0) {                                                                      
 892                 info += DEVINFO_STEP + String.valueOf(record.steps) + "   ";                             
 893             }                                                                                            
 894             if (record.distance > 0) {                                                                   
 895                 info += DEVINFO_DISTANCE + String.valueOf(record.distance) + "   ";                      
 896             }                                                                                            
 897             if (record.calories > 0) {                                                                   
 898                 info += DEVINFO_CALORY + String.valueOf(record.calories) + "   ";                        
 899             }                                                                                            
 900             if (record.heartRate > 0) {                                                                  
 901                 info += DEVINFO_HEART + String.valueOf(record.heartRate) + "   ";                        
 902             }                                                                                            
 903                                                                                                          
 904             if (!info.equals("")) {                                                                      
 905                 getDevice().addDeviceInfo(new GenericItem("", info));                                    
 906             }                                                                                            
 907         } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {                                                           
 908             LOG.info((e.getMessage()));                                                                  
 909         }                                                                                                
 910     }

 912     private void handleBatteryInfo(byte data) {                                                          
 913             if (batteryCmd.level != (short) data) {                                                      
 914                 batteryCmd.level = (short) data;                                                         
 915                 handleGBDeviceEvent(batteryCmd);                                                         
 916             }                                                                                            
 917     }

 107     @Override                                                                                            
 108     protected TransactionBuilder initializeDevice(TransactionBuilder builder) {                          
 109         LOG.info("Initializing");                                                                        
 110         gbDevice.setState(GBDevice.State.INITIALIZING);                                                  
 111         gbDevice.sendDeviceUpdateIntent(getContext());                                                   
 112         measureCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE);           
 113         ctrlCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_CONTROL);              
 114         builder.notify(getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE), true);             
 115         builder.setGattCallback(this);                                                                   
 116         builder.notify(measureCharacteristic, true);                                                     
 117         // Initialize device                                                                             
 118         sendUserInfo(builder);// Sync preferences                                                        
 119                                                                                                          
 120         gbDevice.setState(GBDevice.State.INITIALIZED);                                                   
 121         gbDevice.sendDeviceUpdateIntent(getContext());                                                   
 122         if (syncHelper == null) {                                                                        
 123             syncHelper = new HPlusHandlerThread(getDevice(), getContext(), this);                        
 124             syncHelper.start();                                                                          
 125         }                                                                                                
 126         syncHelper.sync();                                                                               
 127         getDevice().setFirmwareVersion("N/A");                                                           
 128         getDevice().setFirmwareVersion2("N/A");                                                          
 129         requestDeviceInfo(builder);                                                                      
 130         LOG.info("Initialization Done");                                                                 
 131         return builder;                                                                                  
 132     }

 237     private HPlusSupport setSIT(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                        
 238                                                                                                          
 239         //Makibes F68 doesn't like this command.                                                         
 240         //Just ignore.                                                                                   
 241         if (deviceType == DeviceType.MAKIBESF68) {                                                       
 242             return this;                                                                                 
 243         }                                                                                                
 244                                                                                                          
 245         int startTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITStartTime(getDevice().getAddress());                      
 246         int endTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITEndTime(getDevice().getAddress());                          
 247                                                                                                          
 248         Calendar now = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                  
 249                                                                                                          
 250         transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                
 251                 HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_SIT_INTERVAL,                                                     
 252                 (byte) ((startTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                       
 253                 (byte) (startTime % 256),                                                                
 254                 (byte) ((endTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                         
 255                 (byte) (endTime % 256),                                                                  
 256                 0,                                                                                       
 257                 0,                                                                                       
 258                 (byte) ((now.get(Calendar.YEAR) / 256) & 0xff),                                          
 259                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.YEAR) % 256),                                                   
 260                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MONTH) + 1),                                                    
 261                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH)),                                                 
 262                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY)),                                                  
 263                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MINUTE)),                                                       
 264                 (byte) (now.get(Calendar.SECOND)),                                                       
 265                 0,                                                                                       
 266                 0,                                                                                       
 267                 0,                                                                                       
 268                 0                                                                                        
 269                                                                                                          
 270         });                                                                                              
 271         return this;                                                                                     
 272     }

 602     private void showIncomingCall(String name, String rawNumber) {                                       
 603         try {                                                                                            
 604             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("incomingCall");                             
 605             // Enable call notifications                                                                 
 606             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{ HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_INCOMING_CALL, 1 }); 
 607             // Show Call Icon                                                                            
 608             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{ HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_CALL, HPlusCons🔵
 609             if (name != null) {                                                                          
 610                 byte[] msg = new byte[13];                                                               
 611                 // Show call name                                                                        
 612                 for (int i = 0; i < msg.length; i++) {                                                   
 613                     msg[i] = ' ';                                                                        
 614                 }                                                                                        
 615                 byte[] nameBytes = encodeStringToDevice(name);                                           
 616                 for (int i = 0; (i < nameBytes.length) && (i < (msg.length - 1)); i++) {                 
 617                     msg[i + 1] = nameBytes[i];                                                           
 618                 }                                                                                        
 619                 msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT_NAME;                                    
 620                 builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                  
 621                 msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT_NAME_CN;                                 
 622                 builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                  
 623             }                                                                                            
 624             if (rawNumber != null) {                                                                     
 625                 StringBuilder number = new StringBuilder();                                              
 626                 // Clean up number as the device only accepts digits                                     
 627                 for (char c : rawNumber.toCharArray()) {                                                 
 628                     if (Character.isDigit(c)) {                                                          
 629                         number.append(c);                                                                
 630                     }                                                                                    
 631                 }                                                                                        
 632                 byte[] msg = new byte[13];                                                               
 633                 // Show call number                                                                      
 634                 for (int i = 0; i < msg.length; i++) {                                                   
 635                     msg[i] = ' ';                                                                        
 636                 }                                                                                        
 637                 for (int i = 0; (i < number.length()) && (i < (msg.length - 1)); i++) {                  
 638                     msg[i + 1] = ((byte) (number.charAt(i)));                                            
 639                 }                                                                                        
 640                 msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_CALL_NUMBER;                                    
 641                 builder.wait(200);                                                                       
 642                 builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                  
 643             }                                                                                            
 644             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 645         } catch (IOException e) {                                                                        
 646             GB.toast(getContext(), "Error showing incoming call: " + e.getLocalizedMessage(), Toast.LENGT🔵
 647         }                                                                                                
 648     }

 650     private void showText(String title, String body) {                                                   
 651         try {                                                                                            
 652             TransactionBuilder builder = performInitialized("notification");                             
 653             String message = "";                                                                         
 654             if ((title != null) && (title.length() > 0)) {                                               
 655                 message = StringUtils.pad(StringUtils.truncate(title, 16), 16);// Limit title to top row 
 656                                                                                                          
 657             }                                                                                            
 658             if (body != null) {                                                                          
 659                 message += body;                                                                         
 660             }                                                                                            
 661             byte[] messageBytes = encodeStringToDevice(message);                                         
 662             int length = messageBytes.length / 17;                                                       
 663             length = (length > 5) ? 5 : length;                                                          
 664             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{ HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_INCOMING_MESSAGE, HPlusC🔵
 665             int remaining = Math.min(255, (messageBytes.length % 17) > 0 ? length + 1 : length);         
 666             byte[] msg = new byte[20];                                                                   
 667             msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_ACTION_DISPLAY_TEXT;                                             
 668             msg[1] = ((byte) (remaining));                                                               
 669             for (int i = 2; i < msg.length; i++) {                                                       
 670                 msg[i] = ' ';                                                                            
 671             }                                                                                            
 672             int message_index = 0;                                                                       
 673             int i = 3;                                                                                   
 674             for (int j = 0; j < messageBytes.length; j++) {                                              
 675                 msg[i++] = messageBytes[j];                                                              
 676                 if (i == msg.length) {                                                                   
 677                     message_index++;                                                                     
 678                     msg[2] = ((byte) (message_index));                                                   
 679                     builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                              
 680                     msg = msg.clone();                                                                   
 681                     for (i = 3; i < msg.length; i++) {                                                   
 682                         msg[i] = ' ';                                                                    
 683                     }                                                                                    
 684                     if (message_index < remaining) {                                                     
 685                         i = 3;                                                                           
 686                     } else {                                                                             
 687                         break;                                                                           
 688                     }                                                                                    
 689                 }                                                                                        
 690             }                                                                                            
 691             msg[2] = ((byte) (remaining));                                                               
 692             builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, msg);                                                      
 693             performConnected(builder.getTransaction());                                                  
 694         } catch (IOException e) {                                                                        
 695             GB.toast(getContext(), "Error showing device Notification: " + e.getLocalizedMessage(), Toast🔵
 696         }                                                                                                
 697     }

 707     /**                                                                                                  
 708      * HPlus devices accept a subset of GB2312 with some modifications.                                  
 709      * This function will apply a custom transliteration.                                                
 710      * While related to the methods implemented in LanguageUtils. These are specific for HPLUS           
 711      *                                                                                                   
 712      * @param s The String to transliterate                                                              
 713      * @return An array of bytes ready to be sent to the device                                          
 714      */                                                                                                  
 715     private byte[] encodeStringToDevice(String s) {                                                      
 716         List<Byte> outBytes = new ArrayList<Byte>();                                                     
 717         for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {                                                           
 718             Character c = s.charAt(i);                                                                   
 719             byte[] cs;                                                                                   
 720             if (HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.containsKey(c)) {                                        
 721                 cs = HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.get(c);                                             
 722             } else {                                                                                     
 723                 try {                                                                                    
 724                     if (HPlusCoordinator.getUnicodeSupport(this.gbDevice.getAddress())) {                
 725                         cs = c.toString().getBytes("Unicode");                                           
 726                     } else {                                                                             
 727                         cs = c.toString().getBytes("GB2312");                                            
 728                     }                                                                                    
 729                 } catch (UnsupportedEncodingException e) {                                               
 730                     // Fallback. Result string may be strange, but better than nothing                   
 731                     cs = c.toString().getBytes();                                                        
 732                 }                                                                                        
 733             }                                                                                            
 734             for (int j = 0; j < cs.length; j++) {                                                        
 735                 outBytes.add(cs[j]);                                                                     
 736             }                                                                                            
 737         }                                                                                                
 738         return ArrayUtils.toPrimitive(outBytes.toArray(new Byte[outBytes.size()]));                      
 739     }

 741     @Override                                                                                            
 742     public boolean onCharacteristicChanged(BluetoothGatt gatt, BluetoothGattCharacteristic characteristic🔵
 743         if (super.onCharacteristicChanged(gatt, characteristic)) {                                       
 744             return true;                                                                                 
 745         }                                                                                                
 746         UUID characteristicUUID = characteristic.getUuid();                                              
 747         byte[] data = characteristic.getValue();                                                         
 748         if (data.length == 0) {                                                                          
 749             return true;                                                                                 
 750         }                                                                                                
 751         switch (data[0]) {                                                                               
 752             case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION :                                                           
 753             case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION1 :                                                          
 754                 return syncHelper.processVersion(data);                                                  
 755             case HPlusConstants.DATA_STATS :                                                             
 756                 boolean result = syncHelper.processRealtimeStats(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAge());   
 757                 if (result) {                                                                            
 758                     processExtraInfo(data);                                                              
 759                 }                                                                                        
 760                 return result;                                                                           
 761             case HPlusConstants.DATA_SLEEP :                                                             
 762                 return syncHelper.processIncomingSleepData(data);                                        
 763             case HPlusConstants.DATA_STEPS :                                                             
 764                 return syncHelper.processDaySummary(data);                                               
 765             case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY :                                                       
 766             case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY_ALT :                                                   
 767                 return syncHelper.processIncomingDaySlotData(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAge());       
 768             case HPlusConstants.DATA_UNKNOWN :                                                           
 769                 return true;                                                                             
 770             default :                                                                                    
 771                 LOG.info((("Unhandled characteristic change: " + characteristicUUID) + " code: ") + Array🔵
 772                 return true;                                                                             
 773         }                                                                                                
 774     }

 776     private void processExtraInfo(byte[] data) {                                                         
 777         try {                                                                                            
 778             HPlusDataRecordRealtime record = new HPlusDataRecordRealtime(data, HPlusCoordinator.getUserAg🔵
 779             handleBatteryInfo(record.battery);                                                           
 780             String DEVINFO_STEP = getContext().getString(R.string.chart_steps) + ": ";                   
 781             String DEVINFO_DISTANCE = getContext().getString(R.string.distance) + ": ";                  
 782             String DEVINFO_CALORY = getContext().getString(R.string.calories) + ": ";                    
 783             String DEVINFO_HEART = getContext().getString(R.string.charts_legend_heartrate);             
 784             String info = "";                                                                            
 785             if (record.steps > 0) {                                                                      
 786                 info += (DEVINFO_STEP + String.valueOf(record.steps)) + "   ";                           
 787             }                                                                                            
 788             if (record.distance > 0) {                                                                   
 789                 info += (DEVINFO_DISTANCE + String.valueOf(record.distance)) + "   ";                    
 790             }                                                                                            
 791             if (record.calories > 0) {                                                                   
 792                 info += (DEVINFO_CALORY + String.valueOf(record.calories)) + "   ";                      
 793             }                                                                                            
 794             if (record.heartRate > 0) {                                                                  
 795                 info += (DEVINFO_HEART + String.valueOf(record.heartRate)) + "   ";                      
 796             }                                                                                            
 797             if (!info.equals("")) {                                                                      
 798                 getDevice().addDeviceInfo(new GenericItem("", info));                                    
 799             }                                                                                            
 800         } catch (java.lang.IllegalArgumentException e) {                                                 
 801             LOG.info(e.getMessage());                                                                    
 802         }                                                                                                
 803     }

  97          addSupportedService(HPlusConstants.UUID_SERVICE_HP);

 116      @Override                                                                                                     
 117      protected TransactionBuilder initializeDevice(TransactionBuilder builder) {                                   
 118          LOG.info("Initializing");                                                                                 
 119                                                                                                                    
 120          builder.add(new SetDeviceStateAction(getDevice(), GBDevice.State.INITIALIZING, getContext()));            


 121                                                                                                                    
 122          measureCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE);                    
 123          ctrlCharacteristic = getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_CONTROL);                       
 124                                                                                                                    
 125          getDevice().setFirmwareVersion("N/A");                                                                    
 126          getDevice().setFirmwareVersion2("N/A");                                                                   
 127                                                                                                                    
 128          syncHelper = new HPlusHandlerThread(getDevice(), getContext(), this);                                     
 129                                                                                                                    
 130          //Initialize device                                                                                       
 131          sendUserInfo(builder); //Sync preferences                                                                 
 132                                                                                                                    
 133                                                                                                                    
 134          requestDeviceInfo(builder);                                                                               
 135                                                                                                                    
 136          setInitialized(builder);                                                                                  
 137                                                                                                                    
 138          syncHelper.start();                                                                                       
 139                                                                                                                    
 140          builder.notify(getCharacteristic(HPlusConstants.UUID_CHARACTERISTIC_MEASURE), true);                      
 141          builder.setGattCallback(this);                                                                            
 142          builder.notify(measureCharacteristic, true);                                                              


















 143                                                                                                                    
 144          return builder;                                                                                           
 145      }

 147      private HPlusSupport sendUserInfo(TransactionBuilder builder) {                                               
 148          builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_PREF_START);                                     
 149          builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_PREF_START1);                                    
 150                                                                                                                    
 151          syncPreferences(builder);                                                                                 
 152                                                                                                                    
 153          builder.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_CONF_END});                           
 154          return this;                                                                                              
 155      }

 157      private HPlusSupport syncPreferences(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                        
 158                                                                                                                    
 159          if (deviceType == DeviceType.HPLUS) {                                                                     
 160              setSIT(transaction);          //Sync SIT Interval                                                     
 161          }                                                                                                         
 162                                                                                                                    
 163          setCurrentDate(transaction);                                                                              
 164          setCurrentTime(transaction);                                                                              
 165          setDayOfWeek(transaction);                                                                                
 166          setTimeMode(transaction);                                                                                 
 167                                                                                                                    
 168          setGender(transaction);                                                                                   
 169          setAge(transaction);                                                                                      
 170          setWeight(transaction);                                                                                   
 171          setHeight(transaction);                                                                                   
 172                                                                                                                    
 173          setGoal(transaction);                                                                                     
 174          setLanguage(transaction);                                                                                 
 175          setScreenTime(transaction);                                                                               
 176          setUnit(transaction);                                                                                     
 177          setAllDayHeart(transaction);                                                                              
 178                                                                                                                    
 179          return this;                                                                                              
 180      }

 211      private HPlusSupport setCurrentDate(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                         
 212          Calendar c = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                             
 213          int year = c.get(Calendar.YEAR);                                                                          
 214          int month = c.get(Calendar.MONTH);                                                                        
 215          int day = c.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH);                                                                   
 216                                                                                                                    
 217          transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                         
 218                  HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_DATE,                                                                      
 219                  (byte) ((year / 256) & 0xff),                                                                     
 220                  (byte) (year % 256),                                                                              
 221                  (byte) (month + 1),                                                                               
 222                  (byte) (day)                                                                                      
 223                                                                                                                    
 224          });                                                                                                       
 225          return this;                                                                                              
 226      }                                                                                                             
 227                                                                                                                    
 228      private HPlusSupport setCurrentTime(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                         
 229          Calendar c = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                             
 230                                                                                                                    
 231          transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                         
 232                  HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_TIME,                                                                      
 233                  (byte) c.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY),                                                               
 234                  (byte) c.get(Calendar.MINUTE),                                                                    
 235                  (byte) c.get(Calendar.SECOND)                                                                     
 236                                                                                                                    
 237          });                                                                                                       
 238          return this;                                                                                              
 239      }

 253      private HPlusSupport setSIT(TransactionBuilder transaction) {                                                 
 254                                                                                                                    
 255          //Makibes F68 doesn't like this command.                                                                  
 256          //Just ignore.                                                                                            
 257          if (deviceType == DeviceType.MAKIBESF68) {                                                                
 258              return this;                                                                                          
 259          }                                                                                                         
 260                                                                                                                    
 261          int startTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITStartTime(getDevice().getAddress());                               
 262          int endTime = HPlusCoordinator.getSITEndTime(getDevice().getAddress());                                   
 263                                                                                                                    
 264          Calendar now = GregorianCalendar.getInstance();                                                           
 265                                                                                                                    
 266          transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{                                                         
 267                  HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_SIT_INTERVAL,                                                              
 268                  (byte) ((startTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                                
 269                  (byte) (startTime % 256),                                                                         
 270                  (byte) ((endTime / 256) & 0xff),                                                                  
 271                  (byte) (endTime % 256),                                                                           
 272                  0,                                                                                                
 273                  0,                                                                                                
 274                  (byte) ((now.get(Calendar.YEAR) / 256) & 0xff),                                                   
 275                  (byte) (now.get(Calendar.YEAR) % 256),                                                            
 276                  (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MONTH) + 1),                                                             
 277                  (byte) (now.get(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH)),                                                          
 278                  (byte) (now.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY)),                                                           
 279                  (byte) (now.get(Calendar.MINUTE)),                                                                
 280                  (byte) (now.get(Calendar.SECOND)),                                                                
 281                  0,                                                                                                
 282                  0,                                                                                                
 283                  0,                                                                                                
 284                  0                                                                                                 
 285                                                                                                                    
 286          });                                                                                                       
 287          return this;                                                                                              
 288      }

 368      private HPlusSupport setAlarm(TransactionBuilder transaction, Calendar t) {                                   
 369                                                                                                                    
 370          byte hour = HPlusConstants.ARG_ALARM_DISABLE;                                                             
 371          byte minute = HPlusConstants.ARG_ALARM_DISABLE;                                                           
 372                                                                                                                    
 373          if (t != null) {                                                                                          
 374              hour = (byte) t.get(Calendar.HOUR_OF_DAY);                                                            
 375              minute = (byte) t.get(Calendar.MINUTE);                                                               
 376          }                                                                                                         
 377                                                                                                                    
 378          transaction.write(ctrlCharacteristic, new byte[]{HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_ALARM,                            
 379                  hour,                                                                                             
 380                  minute});                                                                                         
 381                                                                                                                    
 382          return this;                                                                                              
 383      }

 385      private HPlusSupport setFindMe(TransactionBuilder transaction, boolean state) {                               
 386          //TODO: Find how this works                                                                               
 387                                                                                                                    
 388          byte[] msg = new byte[2];                                                                                 
 389          msg[0] = HPlusConstants.CMD_SET_FINDME;

 393          else

 796      /**                                                                                                           
 797       * HPlus devices accept a subset of GB2312 with some modifications.                                           
 798       * This function will apply a custom transliteration.                                                         
 799       * While related to the methods implemented in LanguageUtils. These are specific for HPLUS                    
 800       *                                                                                                            
 801       * @param s The String to transliterate                                                                       
 802       * @return An array of bytes ready to be sent to the device                                                   
 803       */                                                                                                           
 804      private byte[] encodeStringToDevice(String s) {                                                               
 805                                                                                                                    
 806          List<Byte> outBytes = new ArrayList<Byte>();                                                              
 807                                                                                                                    
 808          for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {                                                                    
 809              Character c = s.charAt(i);                                                                            
 810              byte[] cs;                                                                                            
 811                                                                                                                    
 812              if (HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.containsKey(c)) {                                                 
 813                  cs = new byte[]{HPlusConstants.transliterateMap.get(c)};                                          

 814              } else {                                                                                              
 815                  try {                                                                                             
 816                      if (HPlusCoordinator.getLanguage(this.gbDevice.getAddress()) == HPlusConstants.ARG_LANGUAGE_CN🔵



 817                          cs = c.toString().getBytes("GB2312");                                                     
 818                      else                                                                                          
 819                          cs = c.toString().getBytes("UTF-8");                                                      
 820                  } catch (UnsupportedEncodingException e) {                                                        
 821                      //Fallback. Result string may be strange, but better than nothing                             
 822                      cs = c.toString().getBytes();                                                                 
 823                  }                                                                                                 
 824              }                                                                                                     
 825              for (int j = 0; j < cs.length; j++)                                                                   
 826                  outBytes.add(cs[j]);                                                                              
 827          }                                                                                                         
 828                                                                                                                    
 829          return ArrayUtils.toPrimitive(outBytes.toArray(new Byte[outBytes.size()]));                               
 830      }

 832      @Override                                                                                                     
 833      public boolean onCharacteristicChanged(BluetoothGatt gatt,                                                    
 834                                             BluetoothGattCharacteristic characteristic) {                          
 835          if (super.onCharacteristicChanged(gatt, characteristic)) {                                                
 836              return true;                                                                                          
 837          }                                                                                                         
 838                                                                                                                    
 839          UUID characteristicUUID = characteristic.getUuid();                                                       
 840          byte[] data = characteristic.getValue();                                                                  
 841          if (data.length == 0)                                                                                     
 842              return true;                                                                                          
 843                                                                                                                    
 844          switch (data[0]) {                                                                                        
 845              case HPlusConstants.DATA_VERSION:                                                                     

 846                  return syncHelper.processVersion(data);                                                           
 847                                                                                                                    
 848              case HPlusConstants.DATA_STATS:                                                                       
 849                  boolean result = syncHelper.processRealtimeStats(data);                                           

 850                  if (result) {                                                                                     
 851                      processExtraInfo (data);                                                                      
 852                  }                                                                                                 
 853                  return result;                                                                                    
 854                                                                                                                    
 855              case HPlusConstants.DATA_SLEEP:                                                                       
 856                  return syncHelper.processIncomingSleepData(data);                                                 
 857                                                                                                                    
 858              case HPlusConstants.DATA_STEPS:                                                                       
 859                  return syncHelper.processDaySummary(data);                                                        
 860                                                                                                                    
 861              case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY:                                                                 
 862              case HPlusConstants.DATA_DAY_SUMMARY_ALT:                                                             
 863                  return syncHelper.processIncomingDaySlotData(data);                                               
 864                                                                                                                    



 865              default:                                                                                              
 866                  LOG.info("Unhandled characteristic change: " + characteristicUUID + " code: " + data[0]);         


 867                  return true;                                                                                      
 868          }                                                                                                         
 869      }

 871      private void  processExtraInfo (byte[] data) {                                                                
 872          try {                                                                                                     
 873              HPlusDataRecordRealtime record = new HPlusDataRecordRealtime(data);                                   

 874                                                                                                                    
 875              handleBatteryInfo(record.battery);                                                                    
 876                                                                                                                    
 877              String DEVINFO_STEP = getContext().getString(R.string.chart_steps) + ": ";                            
 878              String DEVINFO_DISTANCE = getContext().getString(R.string.distance) + ": ";                           
 879              String DEVINFO_CALORY = getContext().getString(R.string.calories) + ": ";                             
 880              String DEVINFO_HEART = getContext().getString(R.string.charts_legend_heartrate);                      
 881                                                                                                                    
 882              String info = "";                                                                                     
 883              if (record.steps > 0) {                                                                               
 884                  info += DEVINFO_STEP + String.valueOf(record.steps) + "   ";                                      
 885              }                                                                                                     
 886              if (record.distance > 0) {                                                                            
 887                  info += DEVINFO_DISTANCE + String.valueOf(record.distance) + "   ";                               
 888              }                                                                                                     
 889              if (record.calories > 0) {                                                                            
 890                  info += DEVINFO_CALORY + String.valueOf(record.calories) + "   ";                                 
 891              }                                                                                                     
 892              if (record.heartRate > 0) {                                                                           
 893                  info += DEVINFO_HEART + String.valueOf(record.heartRate) + "   ";                                 
 894              }                                                                                                     
 895                                                                                                                    
 896              if (!info.equals("")) {                                                                               
 897                  getDevice().addDeviceInfo(new GenericItem("", info));                                             
 898              }                                                                                                     
 899          } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {                                                                    
 900              LOG.info((e.getMessage()));                                                                           
 901          }                                                                                                         
 902      }
